sailpoint.object
Class RoleRelationships

java.lang.Object
  sailpoint.object.RoleRelationships

public class RoleRelationships
extends java.lang.Object

Used to represent an analysis of the role relationships for a single identity. This is a transient object used by the UI when displaying assigned and detected roles for an identity. It is built by the Identitizer.
